remarks.format:
  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1eb39-108">В следующем образце кода возвращается тип <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1eb39-108">The following sample returns the type <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebScriptEnablingBehavior>.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System;  
using System.ServiceModel;  
using System.ServiceModel.Web;  
using System.ServiceModel.Configuration;  
  
    class Program  
    {  
        static void Main(string[] args)  
        {  
            WebScriptEnablingElement wSEB = new WebScriptEnablingElement();  
            Console.WriteLine("The type is: {0}",wSEB.BehaviorType );  
            Console.WriteLine("Press <ENTER> to terminate the program.");  
            Console.ReadLine();  
        }  
    }  
```

  
  
